Our Focus


 Chiasma is a biopharmaceutical company focused on improving the lives of patients who face challenges associated with existing treatments for their rare and debilitating diseases. Employing its Transient Permeability Enhancer (TPE®) technology platform, Chiasma is seeking to develop and ultimately commercialize oral medications that are currently only available as injections.  The company is developing octreotide capsules (conditionally trade named Mycapssa®) for the potential treatment of adults with acromegaly.


