Billion Dollar Secret



Company Summary
Chiasma, Inc. is a biopharmaceutical company. The company's TPE(R) technology develops oral peptides and other molecules. Its primary product candidate consists of oral octreotide which is in different clinical trial. Chiasma, Inc. is based in Newton, USA.   

















 




















