Chiasma Inc.


            
            Chiasma, Inc. operates as a pharmaceutical company, which engages in developing and commercializing oral forms of therapies that are available by injection. Its products include octreotide capsules and clinical trials. The company was founded by Shmuel A. Ben-Sasson and Guy Yachin on April 12, 2001 and is headquartered in Waltham, MA.

            
